<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n33023a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n33" href="#n33023a">N33 (VI.B.4)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n33all.htm#n33023a"> 23(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> <u>purgatory</u> </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: PURGATORY (Late Lat. <i>purgatorium</i>, from <i>purgare</i>, to purge), according to Roman Catholic faith, a state of suffering after death in which the souls of those who die in venial sin, and of those who still owe some debt of temporal punishment for mortal sin, are rendered fit to enter heaven. </mm> </dd></dl>
